lyrics:
[verse]
I woke up this morning, feeling the sun's warm embrace
With a heart full of hope, a smile on my face
Destiny's whisper carried on the early breeze
I feel lucky, this day holds all that I need

[chorus]
I feel lucky, lucky like a shooting star
Gonna shine my light, no matter where you are
With each step I take, the world unfolds its charms
I feel lucky, it's time to embrace life's arms
